quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,33,"And the evil of what they do will be apparent to them, and that which they scoff at will besiege them"
  45,34,"And it will be said, \"We forget you today as you forgot your appointment this Day. The Fire shall now be your abode, and none shall come to help you"
  45,35,"That is because you held Allah’≥ Verses/Signs in ridicule and the worldly life deluded you.\" That Day then they shall not be taken out of that (unenviable) state of theirs nor shall they be allowed to solicit favours"
  45,36,"All praise is due then to Allah, the Lord of the heavens, the Lord of the earth, the Lord of the entire Universe"
  45,37,"And all greatness in the heavens and the earth is His! He is the One Omnipotent, Wise"
  46,1,Ha-mim
  46,2,"The Book [Qur'aan] is a revelation from Allah the Omnipotent, Wise"
  46,3,"We created not the heavens and the earth and all that is in between them save with truthful purpose, and for a term appointed. And those who suppress the Truth heed not the warning they are given"
  46,4,"Say, \"Have you considered those that you invoke besides Allah? Show me what part of the earth they have created! Or have they any share in the heavens? Bring me a divine book preceding this one (Qur'aan), or some shred of knowledge in support, if what you say is true"
  46,5,"And who is gone further astray than those who pray, instead of Allah, to such as hear not their prayer till the Day of Resurrection, and are unaware of their prayer"